    "description": "Cadava is a roguelike fantasy game where you must survive the endless challenges of the prisoner plane that you find yourself stuck in. Create a character, upgrade your supplies and spells and compete in the arena at your chance for both glory and copper currency. But beware of the inhabitants of Cadava, as everyone is attempting to earn enough money to buy their freedom and move out of the prisoner district. Some will try to rob you, some will solicit odd jobs to enhance their ability to survive and some will help. Do you have what it takes to amass enough copper to buy your freedom? Only one way to find out...",
